        c: "<p>在传送后的 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">5</span> 秒内你受到的伤害降低 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">25%</span> 。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>26</em></p>",
        d: "<p>在 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">5</span> 秒内再次施放传送将会立即将你传送回初始位置，并使剩余冷却时间缩短至 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">1</span> 秒。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>37</em></p>",
        e: "<p>施放传送后，你可以在 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">3</span> 秒内额外传送 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">1</span> 次。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>31</em></p>",
