        b: "<p>每击中一名敌人即可恢复 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">1</span> 点奥能。</p><p>原力之波的伤害类型转换为闪电伤害。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>39</em></p>",
        c: "<p>使伤害提高至 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">475%</span> 的武器伤害（作为火焰伤害）。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>49</em></p>",
        d: "<p>每击中一名敌人可使你下一个奥术法术的伤害提高 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">4%</span> 。</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>32</em></p>",
