        x: "<div class=\"tooltip-body \"> <span class=\"d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 \" style=\"background-image: url('http://media.blizzard.com/d3/icons/skills/64/wizard_waveofforce.png'); width: 64px; height: 64px;\"> <span class=\"frame\"></span> </span> <div class=\"description\"> <p><span class=\"d3-color-gold\">消耗：</span> <span class=\"d3-color-green\">25</span> 点奥能</p><p>发出一股纯净能量冲击波，对附近的敌人造成 <span class=\"d3-color-green\">390%</span> 的武器伤害（作为奥术伤害）。</p> <p class=\"special\">原力</p> <p class=\"subtle\">Unlocked at level <em>9</em></p> </div> </div>",
